{"Id":486,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-mazhonggang","Author":"Ma Zhong Gang","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://alquran.cloud/api","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"因为他[不信仰者在尘世]不确信[《古兰经》]，不礼拜，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":32,"Text":"而他却否认[《古兰经》和穆圣]，背离真理。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":33,"Text":"然后，他傲慢地回到他的家人那里。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":34,"Text":"你[不信仰者]要遭不幸了！你要遭不幸了！"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"你要遭不幸了！你要遭不幸了！"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"难道人以为他可以放纵[为所欲为而不受惩罚]吗？"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"难道他原不是一滴被射出的精液吗？"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"然后，那滴精液变成一块凝血，然后，他[安拉]创造他并使他匀称。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"他用那滴精液创造了男女两性。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":40,"Text":"难道能这样做的他[安拉]还不能使死者复活吗？[绝对能]。"}]}